location.fullValue: Holbrook Plan, Blacktail at The Meadows

data.description: Charming 2-story home, located on a cul-de-sac in wonderful Red Hawk Subdivision in Castle Rock. Ideal location close to shopping, restaurants, parks, hiking trails and Red Hawk Ridge Golf Course. Spacious open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, beautiful windows and tons of natural light. Main floor features open entry way, gorgeous kitchen with eating area, formal dining room. living room and great room. Upstairs find the light and bright loft, Primary suite with sitting area, walk-in closet and large bathroom, and also 3 additional bedrooms. Huge unfinished basement is ready for your design. Amazing peaceful backyard with beautiful landscaping and deck, perfect for entertaining friends and family and enjoying Colorado sunsets. New light fixtures, blinds and paint throughout, new carpet in formal entry room, dining room, staircase and bedrooms, new flooring in loft, new paint on deck and updated landscaping! Don't miss out on this incredible home!
